== Local installation

=== OSX, Linux

Something like:
[source,shell]
--------------------
$ git clone git://github.com/tricycle/predictionbook.git
$ cd predictionbook
$ git submodule update --init
$ cp config/database.example.yml config/database.yml
$ rake gems:install
$ RAILS_ENV=test rake gems:install
$ RAILS_ENV=cucumber rake gems:install
$ rake db:schema:load
--------------------
